title: I want to switch to server Vietnam

replies.body:
Garena operates and supports a Vietnamese server, so transferring to it is not possible from NA, nor can we provide support for their server. 

For more information, check out our [Account Transfer FAQ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751924-Account-Transfer-FAQ) and [Garena Vietnam.](http://www.garena.vn/) Let me know if you have any questions.

http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/BEUGEmnQ-vietnamese-account-transfer

Check out this board post from awhile ago! Tell me if it works.
